				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				&quot;EVERLORE/GEORGIA. Rather than complaining that people are picking on you, your website is based on the success or failure of this game. You may want to act as a spokesperson for the disenchanted players of everquest. You could do this by polling your web community and submitting the results to Sony/Verant. This would elleviate people from attacking you, and probably curry favor with much of the EQ community. More people will hear about how you are looking out for the welfare of the players and quite possibly you will see in an increase in hits on your web site. &quot;<BR>
<BR>
1. Georgia is responsible for what happens, so just because she volunteers on a fan site about EverQuest in no way entitles you all to ***** and moan about the bad things that happen.<BR>
<BR>
2. I'm sure if Verant/SOE cared enough for the poll results, they'd run it themselves.<BR>
<BR>
3. If you haven't noticed, this sight slows down once in awhile because on a good time, there are 11,000 users cruising the site.. there's not much need to worry about hits.<BR>
